==German==
===Etymology===
From an old word ''ossenpesek'' [[pizzle]] (2), related to ''pese'' "[[tendon]]", ''peserik'' "[[penis]]". A pizzle was used back then to beat man and animal.

===Verb===
'''piesacken'''
# to [[badger]] (annoy badly)
#:''Hör auf, deine kleine Schwester zu '''piesacken'''!''
